title: Week 14 NFL Recap, Analysis; 49ers-Saints Game of the Year, Pats screwed by refs (Football 12/9)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 14 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 14 games on the Sunday slate including Chiefs-Patriots (1:00), 49ers-Saints (23:00), Seahawks-Rams (37:00), Redskins-Packers and Lions-Vikings (50:00), Titans-Raiders (1:00:30), Ravens-Bills (1:08:30), Broncos-Texans (1:15:15), Steelers-Cardinals (1:21:15), Bengals-Browns (1:34:00), Panthers-Falcons (1:41:20), Colts-Bucs (1:44:45), Dolphins-Jets (1:50:00) and Chargers-Jags (1:55:10).
